quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  112,1,"Maaku-aan nelaa…óo- ko Kanko woni gooto e Alliyankaagal, alah dewatee e goongo si wona Kanko."
  112,2,"Ko kanko woni koohoowo mbo koongu haa…óti nder sifaaji timmal e njoo…óndam, Mbo tagaa…ìe paandato."
  112,3,"Oon mbo jibinaani O jibinaaka,O jibinaani hay gooto,O alah …ìi…ì…ó…óo-Kanko cenii…óo O- O alah jiknaa…óo."
  112,4,"Woodanaani Mbo pasa hay gooto."
  113,1,"Maaku-aan nelaa…óo- mbe…óa moolo e jom subaka mbe…óa hoddinoo mbo."
  113,2,"E bone ko lorata tagoore nde."
  113,3,"Mbe…óa moolo e Alla e bone …ìanngoowo jemma ummaade daabe e banndi en."
  113,4,"Mbe…óa e moolo Makko e bone wilee…ìe wuttoo…ìe e pi…ìle."
  113,5,"Mbe…óa moolo e bone haaside si o golli ko faanata mbo e haasidaagal."
  114,1,"Maaku-aan nelaa…óo- mbe…óa moolo e jom yim…ìe mbe…óa hoddinoo mbo."
  114,2,"Laam…óo yim…ìe, hombo firlito e mum en no O faalira, alah laam…óo tanah Makko."
  114,3,"Dewetee…óo mum en e goongo, alah dewetee…óo e goongo mbo wonah Makko."
  114,4,"E bone seytaneeji cikkinooji si o welsandiima innude Alla, o leeli siftorde Mbo."
  114,5,"Hombo werlo sikkeeli makko e …ìer…óe yim…ìe."
  114,6,"…óum wonata ko e yim…ìe hono …óum wonrata e jinneeji."